lyrics:
[Verse]
In the morning light, I'm feeling blue
Lost in emotions, don't know what to do
But deep down inside, I know I'll get through
These tears might fall, but I'll make it, it's true

[Chorus]
When I'm down, I'll rise again
With strength inside, I'll find my zen
Through the darkest night, I'll find my way
I won't give up, I'll make it, come what may
